  "description": "A color change detection task dataset organized in BIDS format. This raw intracranial EEG dataset contains electrophysiological recordings from participants performing a visual perception task involving color discrimination. Participants viewed stimuli and detected changes in color, providing a controlled paradigm for investigating visual processing and perceptual decision-making in human intracranial recordings. The dataset is intended to support research in visual processing, cognitive neuroscience, and intracranial electrophysiology.",
